{"tid":965583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【打尖拒認錯　大陸婆照嘟卡　醒目客一招誘落車】","createTime":"2019-01-02T07:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T14:08:46.000Z","uid":225464,"like":631,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"5db0725f9c155b3288af073d95558468349427d8","tid":965583,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:15:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190102/bkn-20190102135052190-0102_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190102%2Fbkn-20190102135052190-0102_00822_001.html&d=cFyyBEaL9oyRSxvD5eL3%2B54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=94f70521\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190102/bkn-20190102135052190-0102_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jnYeZmr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjnYeZmr.jpg&h=927f8bfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>打尖拒認錯　大媽照嘟卡　醒目客一招誘落車</strong><br />\n<br />\n排隊是維持秩序的良好方法，惟近日有大媽打尖衝上小巴，更拍卡坐低，結果被司機乘客齊心驅趕，更設計迫她落車。<br />\n<br />\n有乘客在其Facebook專頁「哈弟Hadee─我由乜乜徒步到乜乜」講述事件，指星期二（1日）凌晨近3時正在荃灣等於小巴，當時站頭有約50人正排隊候車。未料當小巴到站時，有一名操普通話的婦人突然祟出並衝上小巴。司機即時大聲喝止︰「排隊呀」！<br />\n<br />\n她聲稱自己有排隊，但司機激動地反駁︰「望住你打尖啦，後面排緊咁多人你見唔到㗎？呢度係香港，唔係大陸，落番去排隊啦」！<br />\n<br />\n但大媽卻厚着臉皮，取出八達通拍卡並坐下，司機只好熄匙堅持不開車，批評大媽是「慣犯」，每日如是。全車乘客亦團結一致，齊聲斥︰「落車啦你」。<br />\n<br />\n未料大媽仍然無動於衷，並說︰「我不怕你們」、「你打我唄」、「我頭痛呀」。有肥仔乘客遂搶走大媽手上的電話，衝落車放在地上。<br />\n<br />\n「阿姐要喺小巴同手機之間做選擇，佢兩樣都想要，所以企喺車門樓梯，係咁大叫︰『把手機還我』」。最終在無人幫忙下，她被迫妥協，「佢離開架車嗰刻，司機極速撻匙開車，阿姐轉身粗口都講唔切，我哋已經掰掰佢條尾」。<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛讚揚司機及車上乘客非常團結︰「正氣司機和肥仔好波」、「終於有人出聲」、「呢啲就係香港精神囉」！"},{"pid":"293597c5fd0e36c7a33b1591f1570b1157d0c729","tid":965583,"uid":124107,"like":150,"dislike":3,"score":147,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:17:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e751eb06e0d114319ca5b33c3ede689a9dd6bf1d","tid":965583,"uid":10606,"like":177,"dislike":0,"score":177,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:17:51.000Z","msg":"個肥仔好野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c481af4194ca68b14958c6820b8043132d98484a","tid":965583,"uid":157197,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:18:05.000Z","msg":"啲大媽真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係想見一隻摑一隻"},{"pid":"c79d139a51fbab1e3101506a28d1eb0f5dec289d","tid":965583,"uid":107364,"like":5,"dislike":130,"score":-125,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:18:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5160a8c5ae59b9f9f32e07245d24c2c0257f7afc","tid":965583,"uid":213441,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:24:21.000Z","msg":"殺光支那狗唔係無講錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a76e9d1577e59e38161c4493d7c6595483fa55","tid":965583,"uid":224510,"like":9,"dislike":93,"score":-84,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:26:07.000Z","msg":"肥仔好波<br />\n但犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb3c55534bd70ff10ebea8b93c9d4b46f45aa81","tid":965583,"uid":154221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:26:56.000Z","msg":"肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb67710ba2ea95e433f20d56f8200e100bcb6fd9","tid":965583,"uid":122134,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"quote":{"pid":"293597c5fd0e36c7a33b1591f1570b1157d0c729","tid":965583,"uid":124107,"like":150,"dislike":3,"score":147,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:17:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:27:57.000Z","msg":"邊個話<br />\n<br />\n無恥真係天下無敵<br />\n如果唔係有肥仔咁做...<br />\n香港人咁林善 真係吹佢唔漲"},{"pid":"c56480dcbdaac4ad5ac04dc91f37040855902030","tid":965583,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:28:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b984a202ee983c306afd735bcc726855d9ac5f90","tid":965583,"uid":124107,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:28:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc5aee43fead42237379f17bd973ab4978f98a48","tid":965583,"uid":103693,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"74a76e9d1577e59e38161c4493d7c6595483fa55","tid":965583,"uid":224510,"like":9,"dislike":93,"score":-84,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:26:07.000Z","msg":"肥仔好波<br />\n但犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:28:42.000Z","msg":"好似有意圖永久剝削物主擁有權(之類)先叫盜竊<br />\n佢拎左部電話放落地叫蝗婦落車拎好似唔算?<br />\n<br />\n利申唔熟法律"},{"pid":"ae318c821f6feaf58f361639252221ab90515aec","tid":965583,"uid":49994,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:29:18.000Z","msg":"車錢都蝕埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adc98b6b53b6efc0adaa233d55cf100a85ee2ed","tid":965583,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"74a76e9d1577e59e38161c4493d7c6595483fa55","tid":965583,"uid":224510,"like":9,"dislike":93,"score":-84,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:26:07.000Z","msg":"肥仔好波<br />\n但犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:29:44.000Z","msg":"證據？"},{"pid":"fa602aa6338d215ac252c983f10cb8941121fb0d","tid":965583,"uid":122217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa76d6f85b4ea2cee3d4e4840b9d959be71d8932","tid":965583,"uid":22701,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"1adc98b6b53b6efc0adaa233d55cf100a85ee2ed","tid":965583,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"74a76e9d1577e59e38161c4493d7c6595483fa55","tid":965583,"uid":224510,"like":9,"dislike":93,"score":-84,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:26:07.000Z","msg":"肥仔好波<br />\n但犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:29:44.000Z","msg":"證據？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:37:31.000Z","msg":"同支那人講法律真係得談笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebbb75de91709a862b4b8d7a5cd66911a7608c5","tid":965583,"uid":120402,"like":1,"dislike":34,"score":-33,"quote":{"pid":"dc5aee43fead42237379f17bd973ab4978f98a48","tid":965583,"uid":103693,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"74a76e9d1577e59e38161c4493d7c6595483fa55","tid":965583,"uid":224510,"like":9,"dislike":93,"score":-84,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:26:07.000Z","msg":"肥仔好波<br />\n但犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:28:42.000Z","msg":"好似有意圖永久剝削物主擁有權(之類)先叫盜竊<br />\n佢拎左部電話放落地叫蝗婦落車拎好似唔算?<br />\n<br />\n利申唔熟法律"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:39:56.000Z","msg":"盜竊未必入 但普通襲擊就應該係"},{"pid":"fef3fcf11f36b98934e9dd39e72129e0ea9cc360","tid":965583,"uid":228051,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T07:41:15.000Z","msg":"班大媽廢老真係欺善怕惡<br />\n有朝搭小巴，都係幾十人排緊隊，架車一到有個大媽係遠方跑過黎想一野衝上去<br />\n我見勢就攝個身位攔住佢好聲氣同佢講: 條隊係後面排隊呀唔該<br />\n佢同我講: 我有排隊呀你睇唔到咩? <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朝早未訓醒個人特別燥忍唔住爆佢: 屌你老母當我地盲嫁，好聲好氣比個台你唔撚識落，係要咁撚無恥既，知唔知個醜字點寫，行撚開啦<br />\n跟手我就上車，都有心理準備要嘈一輪，點知後面既乘客全部都＂得＂住佢唔比佢上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class